Subject: Re: [T2] Engine won't idle after top end rebuild - need help 

I would suspect a vacuum leak.  Recheck all the hose connections. Get 
yourself a can of Berryman's Carb Cleaner (or equivalent) and spray in 
on the likely suspects and see if the idle smooths out.

